@buildingId = 1
@imageUrl = /api/images/example.jpg

### 1. ItemPost 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items/post/create
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "type": "LOST",
  "category": "UMBRELLA",
  "color": "BLACK",
  "title": "검은 지갑을 찾습니다",
  "description": "공학관 근처에서 분실했습니다.",
  "image_url": "{{imageUrl}}",
  "building_id": {{buildingId}},
  "detail_address": "305호 앞"
}

### 2. ItemPost 목록 조회
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/items/post/list?page=0&size=20
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "category": "UMBRELLA"
}

### 3. ItemPost 단건 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/items/post/list/1
